ca.ualberta.cs.xpertsapp.model

Class User

  • java.lang.Object
    • ca.ualberta.cs.xpertsapp.model.User
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    IObservable

    public class User
extends java.lang.Object
implements IObservable
    This class is used to internally represent a real life user of this digital application for android. Some functions run in O(1) time (maybe) and others do not. Pl0x only have one instance of user representing a person at any given time. Use the user managers to manage users plz. DO NOT CREATE USERS ON YOUR OWN
